<center>
<div id="solutionsHeader" style="background-color:#89d2d4;cursor: hand; cursor: pointer;" onclick="changeSolution('solutionsGrow')">
	Grow!
</div>
<div id="solutionsHeader" style="background-color:#d8549b;cursor: hand; cursor: pointer;" onclick="changeSolution('solutionsFeatured')">
	Be Featured
</div>
<div id="solutionsHeader" style="background-color:#6ebe46;cursor: hand; cursor: pointer;" onclick="changeSolution('solutionsFaq')">
	FAQ
</div>
</center>
<div id="solutionsWrapper" style="padding:20px 20px 20px 20px;">
	
	<div id="solutionsGrow" class="">
		<img src="/assets/grow.png" style="margin-left:20px;">
		
	</div>
	
	<div id="solutionsFeatured" class="hideField">
		<div style="float:left;width:300px;border-right:2px dashed #88d2d2;font-size:18px;padding:0 20px 0 0;">
			<h2 class="greenh2">Have A Business?</h2>
			NytLife can attract thousands of potential new customers through your door.
			
			<h2 class="greenh2">How to work with NytLife</h2>
			It's as easy as filling out the form to the right. We will contact you within one business day.
		</div>
		<div id="requestInfo">
			<img src="/assets/startYourNyt.png">
			<%= form_tag(:action => 'requestInfo') do %>
				<%= text_field(:lead, :first_name, :value => 'First Name', :onclick => 'if(this.value == "First Name"){this.value = ""}', :onblur => 'if(this.value == ""){this.value = "First Name"}')%><br>
				<%= text_field(:lead, :last_name, :value => 'Last Name', :onclick => 'if(this.value == "Last Name"){this.value = ""}', :onblur => 'if(this.value == ""){this.value = "Last Name"}')%><br>
				<%= text_field(:lead, :company_name, :value => 'Company Name', :onclick => 'if(this.value == "Company Name"){this.value = ""}', :onblur => 'if(this.value == ""){this.value = "Company Name"}')%><br>
				<%= text_field(:lead, :phone, :value => 'Phone Number', :onclick => 'if(this.value == "Phone Number"){this.value = ""}', :onblur => 'if(this.value == ""){this.value = "Phone Number"}')%><br>
				<%= text_field(:lead, :email, :value => 'E-Mail', :onclick => 'if(this.value == "E-Mail"){this.value = ""}', :onblur => 'if(this.value == ""){this.value = "E-Mail"}')%><br>
				<%= submit_tag("SUBMIT", :class => 'requestInfoSubmit')%>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<div id="solutionsFaq" style="display:none;">
		<h3>How does NytLife make money?</h3>
		NytLife requires an advertising fee for the promotion of the deal. In most cases, the fee is 
		assessed by the percentage of revenue generated by the deal. 

		<h3>How much does it cost to be featured on NytLife?</h3>
		There is no up front cost involved to be featured on NytLife.

		<h3>Can I limit the number of NytLife vouchers I sell?</h3>
		Each deal is “build to suite” with your particular goals in mind. 

		<h3>When do I get paid?</h3>
		Payment is in thirds for the majority of merchants—34% after 10–14 days, 
		33% after one month, and 33% after two months.

		<h3>What is the NytLife Process?</h3>
		You provide your deal; we provide the rest from graphic design
		 to the end sale. 

		<h3>How do customers find out when I’m running a NytLife deal?</h3>
		Customers can search for nearby bars and clubs with ease via 
		our website & mobile app. Utilizing location and preference 
		options it allows us to highlight 
		your facility and it’s current deal.  

		<h3>May I run multiple deals at the same time?</h3>
		You may have multiple deals; deals may vary in the form of amount, location, and time.
		
	</div>

</div>

<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8">
	function changeSolution(solution){
		document.getElementById('solutionsFeatured').style.display='none';
		document.getElementById('solutionsGrow').style.display='none';
		document.getElementById('solutionsFaq').style.display='none';
		document.getElementById(solution).style.display='block';
	}
</script>